{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But things pretty well remained peaceful from a child's perspective.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of the things I'm telling you is-- is things I learned later on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but putting myself from my vantage point, I would say things were pretty well stable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All-- all-- all that changed was a heightened nervous tension at home because of my parents' anxieties about their families in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and then they're starting to speak their own native language, which so we shouldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the main change at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now the big change occurred on May 10 when all of a sudden, shooting started, bombs were flying, planes would came over, and before we saw-- we knew it, the Germans rolled into the-- into the area.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was always a prized possession for all-- all armies throughout history because being such an important seaport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So because of the rumors, whoever could afford transportation fled.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the big change was that we all-- we all packed up, rented a little truck, put our possessions on it, and tried to escape in front of the-- the troops.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then we got into France, and everybody was on these roads south.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And mainly towards the-- there was a French coast to be able to get over to England.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then we ran into the retreating Allied troops-- British troops-- on the way to Dunkirk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And roads-- roads simply got so clogged that it wasn't even funny.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember how we-- we-- we ate from buying eggs and-- from farms on the way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one day, the Germans caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I recall the first German I ever saw, officer, was a-- a military policeman on a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they call them the-- the-- the Feldgendarmerie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had special uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
